# Container SAST baseline — epic #448 / TRK-311 (Layer 1).
# Build context: helm/federation-gateway/audit-sidecar/. The Dockerfile only
# COPYs from build stages (COPY --from=...), so nothing from the host context
# enters the image; this baseline is a uniform hygiene floor that also keeps
# any stray .env / *.log out of the context upload.
/.git/
/.github/
/scripts/
/tests/
/docs/
*.md
*.log
.env*
